ing: 1 (1 ounce) package McCormickÂ® Guacamole Seasoning Mix
2 ripe avocados - peeled, pitted, and mashed
des: "Two snack time favorites in one show-stopping dip: Guacamole Hummus. California avocados, hummus and one packet of McCormick Guacamole SeasoningÂ are all you need to bring this creamy, savory dip to the table. Serve with pita chips for dipping."
ins:
Stir Seasoning Mix and mashed avocados in medium bowl until well blended. Stir in hummus. Cover surface with plastic wrap.
Refrigerate 30 minutes to allow flavors to blend. Stir before serving. Serve with pita chips or tortilla chips.
